Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇねぇ　ちーちゃん見て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい　何の設備だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:17.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,暇だね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,暇だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　先頭の方に行ってみようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごいことに気がついた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちって　走ってる列車の上に乗って走ってるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それが？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,つまり　いつもよりすごい速さで走ってることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　それは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでって言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:19.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもそもそも私たちは自転する地球の上を走ってるわけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さらにすごい速度かもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じてん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,自転とはつまり　地球が回っていること
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,向きが違うかもしれないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それはどのくらいの速さなの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:40.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,正確な数字は分からないけど　１日で地球を１周する速さだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,マジかよ　速すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あ　ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:51.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ私たちは毎日地球を１周してたってこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうとも言えるな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヤバすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヤバいのはお前の頭だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヤバすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たまに見かけるようになったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり動かないね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,機械の死体か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか前に見た墓を思い出すよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この列車も黒くて箱みたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,移動式の墓って…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一体どこに向かってるんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　これ見て　変な機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,時計か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,とけい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,時間が分かるやつだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:54.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,確か地球が１回転すると針が２回転するんだったような
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,地球より速いな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,時間に速いとか遅いとかないから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　あったっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.23,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく地球は回り　時間は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら行くぞ　早く乗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　ちょっと待ってよ　もう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,せっかちなんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:21.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,走ってる列車の上で急いでもしょうがないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:23.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,回ってる地球の上で急いでもしょうがないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　それは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人はみんな時計を身につけていたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃ便利だからだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:47.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何時までにこれをしなきゃとかそういうことの目安になるし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,便利というか　なんか面倒くさそうだなー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,急ぐのは苦手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもユー　私たちだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,着いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここで終わりじゃないみたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,レーションみたいのが並んでるね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たぶん点滅してるのが現在地だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだたくさんあるね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:30.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,降りないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,時間の話だけどさ　ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:42.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちだって「食料」っていう時間の制約があるんだからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,軽いなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　食料があるうちに　どんどん進んじゃおうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういうことだ　行けるとこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずいぶん長いこと乗ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの列車かなり遠くまで来た気がするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.73,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね　なんかめちゃくちゃ寝た気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　寝てる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:19.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか聞こえるような
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,聞こえるって何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつから音がした気がするんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,墓で拾った変な機械なんだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　あれか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,って　ちゃんと返してって言ったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやー　これ使えそうだったし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,死んだ人のだから罰が当たるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもほら「死人に武器なし」って言うし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,「口なし」だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,素手なら怖くねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,素手でも怖いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで　どんな音が聞こえるの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,不思議な音だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の声に似てるけど　少し違って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:05.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨音のような　「あーあー」って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,リズム？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　リズムってやつがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:16.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな「あーあー　あーあー　あー」って感じ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それは「歌」ってやつなのかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:20.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うた？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の声でやる音楽だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も時々やってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここはくらーい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,くらいなー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,みたいな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうそう　それが歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うた　これが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:46.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっとその機械見せてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:51.71,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あーい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:00.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たぶん電波か何かを受信する機械だと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか悲しい感じがしたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音楽って悲しくなったりするものなんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:15.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,聴いてたらなんか悲しいような気持ちになった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:32.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨音の音楽を聴いた時は少し楽しくなったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,悲しくなったり　楽しくなったり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.94,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音楽というやつにはそういう力があるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,リズムがあるから？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,リズムか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:55.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音波というものにはそもそも波のリズムがあったと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さっき言ってた電波ってやつは？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,電波はよく分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それも何かの波だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,光も波の仲間らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　光も見てて楽しくなったりするのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,街灯を見て楽しくは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:15.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　そろそろ日の光が見たいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:39.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この階層に来てから　ずっと基盤の中だったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの列車でどれくらい移動したのかも分からないし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ひとまず地上部に出なきゃいけないんだろうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく上の方に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上かー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　あれは？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,急な坂だな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おお　動いた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:22.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか速くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　これちゃんと止まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:35.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの音楽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,地上が近いかも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:43.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,近いというか　もう見えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,マジか　速いな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　スイッチスイッチ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どれだろう　よく分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ホントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:20.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんとなく悲しい音楽だね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　見て
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕日だね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤いね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,赤いな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:38.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この赤い光が　なんとなく悲しい色に思えるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この音楽のせいか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それとも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと夕日の赤も悲しいリズムなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,光の…波のリズムか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕日が目に染みる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなに悲しいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいや　痛い　擦りむいた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,気持ちいい日だねー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いい景色にいい音楽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,鳴ってないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,天気は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　動くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:59.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でかい穴だなー　どうやってできたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんなもんかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,毛先が大分ぼさぼさになってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さっぱりしたな　私もユーも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと切りすぎたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんも変わってないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,チーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　穴に降りてみようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだな　水の音もするし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.83,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,降りられるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここもずいぶん武器が落ちてるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱりひどい戦いがあったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この穴もその戦いでできたとか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,穴の内側にも砲台があったりするところを見ると
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この穴ができたのはもっとずっと昔なのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと昔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:09.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　ずーっと昔の戦いでこの大きな穴ができて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:14.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,その周りにできた街で　また戦いが…とか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ややこしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,つめてー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何やってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,冷てぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あそこでご飯にしようか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:47.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,イモを焼いたやつもたくさんあった気がするのに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だいぶ減ってきたね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,髪の毛は切ればさっぱりするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっちがなくなるのは寂しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うめー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:04.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの水溜まりの中に魚でもいればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:10.51,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べたかったなぁ　あの水槽の魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:16.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,助けたいとか言ってたくせに　結局食べたかったのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それはそれ　これはこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,共感してたくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:27.29,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,それかさ　こういう穴から食べ物が出てこないかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,水だけじゃなくてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,出てくるわけないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:39.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,変な生き物が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,生き物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,中　この中に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,生き物って　魚とか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:54.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ううん　もっと違う何か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　ちょっと叩いてみてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　私が？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー　大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫っぽい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:21.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだろう　確かに魚とかじゃなさそうだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.68,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本で見たような
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ね…猫とかか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　食べよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,トカカ…チョテ…マトヨ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:39.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　今その機械から声がしなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　声？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,エ…コ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まさかこいつが喋ってるんじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この猫が？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,猫かどうかは分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　猫　お前は猫なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ぬ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ぬこだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ただ繰り返してるだけじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコダッテ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,焼く？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.75,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,待てって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,テ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やっぱり置いていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　なんで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,言葉を喋るようなのは食べられないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,共感ってやつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.36,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.85,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほかには特に何もないみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:08.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかついてくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　やっぱり食べるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:25.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんていうかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いろいろなくなっていくばっかだし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たまには増やしてみるのもいいかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:42.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいんじゃない？ついてきたいみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもやっぱりユーが運んでくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　かわいいのにー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,柔らけー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんまりいじめるなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:37.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな感じか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.39,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　下手だな
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 快看
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好厉害 这到底是什么设施啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.91,0:03:17.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好无聊啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.88,0:03:30.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没意思
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 我们去前面看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我发现了一个令人震惊的事实
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们现在不是在飞驰的列车上行驶吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.71,0:04:02.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那又怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.00,0:04:06.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们的行驶速度要比平时快得多
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这可不对
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这我要怎么解释啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.69,0:04:19.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 要知道我们一直在自转中的地球表面行驶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.72,0:04:21.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以实际的速度可能会更快
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.63,0:04:24.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,自转？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,自转就是指地球旋转
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过转的方向可能会不一样
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,转动速度有多快呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.00,0:04:40.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,具体的速度我说不上 我只知道地球是一天转一圈
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的假的 这也太快了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.80,0:04:51.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是说我们每天都会绕地球转一圈？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也可以这么理解
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可怕的是你的脑袋瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这种机器越来越常见了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可还是没一台能动啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.53,0:05:19.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,机器的残骸吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你不觉得跟之前去过的墓地有点像吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这个列车也是黑色的 也很像盒子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,移动墓地…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这车到底会开去哪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看 这里有个奇怪的机器
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是钟吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,钟？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是那种会告诉我们时间的东西吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.05,0:05:54.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没记错的话 地球每转一圈 钟上的针就会转两圈
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那不是比地球还要快吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,时间没有快慢的概念
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不对 应该是有的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.79,0:06:07.23,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,总之 地球在不停转动 时间又在不断流逝
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别发呆了 要走了 快上车
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 等我一下嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真性急
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.40,0:06:21.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在行驶的列车上着急有用吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.43,0:06:23.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在旋转的地球上着急 也是没有一丁点用的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不对 这就说错了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,听说以前的人都会随身佩带手表
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为很方便吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.08,0:06:47.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这样就能安排时间 知道该在什么时候做完什么事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,哪里方便了 我倒觉得好麻烦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢赶着做事
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过小尤 我们也…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到了？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这里好像不是终点
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这排灯看着还真像压缩粮呢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.03,0:07:27.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,闪烁着的应该是我们目前的位置
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还有好多地方啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.90,0:07:30.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不下车吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说起时间啊 小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.96,0:07:42.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,对我们来说 食物其实就是种时间上的制约
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,竟然满不在乎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那我们就趁现在还有吃的 不断前进吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没错 能走多远走多远
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.62,0:08:55.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们坐了好长时间啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那趟车估计把我们送到了很远的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.73,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊 感觉睡了一辈子
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.00,0:09:19.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉听到了什么声音
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,听到了什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉这玩意有发出声音
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是以前在墓地捡到的奇怪机器
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.29,0:09:34.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那时候我不是跟你说了要放回去的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我是觉得 这东西可能会派上用场
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,拿死者的东西 小心遭报应
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好「死人又不会开枪」
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是「不会说话」
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,赤手空拳的鬼没什么好怕
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么说都是鬼好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以 你到底听见了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,很神奇的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.09,0:10:01.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有点像人的声音 但又有点区别
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.92,0:10:05.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就像雨声一样 「啊~啊~」的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.92,0:10:06.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,节奏？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,对 有节奏
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.12,0:10:16.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是「啊~啊~ 啊~啊~ 啊~」 像这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那有可能是歌吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.40,0:10:20.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,歌？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是用人的声音来演绎的音乐
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你不就经常会唱吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这里好黑啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就像这样？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没错 这就是歌
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来这就是歌啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.76,0:10:46.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,让我看看那个机器
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.97,0:10:51.71,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.43,0:11:00.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我觉得这应该是一种能接收电波的机器
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那个声音听上去好悲伤
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,音乐能传递悲伤的感情吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.09,0:11:15.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,反正一听那个声音 就会觉得心里挺悲伤的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 确实是这道理
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.46,0:11:32.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,上次听雨点音乐时 就觉得有点开心
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,既会让人悲伤 也会让人开心
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.94,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,或许音乐真的有这样的力量吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为有节奏？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,节奏吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.89,0:11:55.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,声波倒的确是一种有节奏的波动
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那你刚才说的电波呢
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,电波我就不太清楚了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该也是某种波吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,然后光好像也是一种波
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那 看见光也会让人觉得开心吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看着路灯的时候…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.97,0:12:15.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不好说吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 有点怀念阳光了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.07,0:12:39.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,自从来到这一层 我们就一直在基底层里转
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也不知道那趟列车到底带我们走了多远
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,总之 我们得先到地面上去
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么上去？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只能尽量往上走了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,往上啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.51,0:12:55.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 那是什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.40,0:13:15.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好陡的坡啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,按这个吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 动起来了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.11,0:13:22.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不觉得有点快吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 这东西能停下来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.28,0:13:35.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是那首歌
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们应该快到地面了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.72,0:13:43.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是快了 是都能看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的假的 好快啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 快按开关
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,该按哪个呢 不太清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 你没事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.45,0:14:20.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这首歌是挺悲伤的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 快看
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是夕阳
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好红啊
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是挺红的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.84,0:14:38.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看着这红色的光会觉得心里好悲伤
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是因为听了这首歌吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还是说…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.52,0:14:48.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,夕阳的红色应该也是种悲伤的节奏
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.65,0:14:52.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,光的…光波的节奏吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,夕阳好刺眼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有这么悲伤吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 好疼 擦破皮了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,今天真舒服
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,风景好 音乐又好听
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,根本没响好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,天气…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不知道好不好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好了 别动了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.34,0:15:59.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大的洞啊 到底是怎么形成的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,虽然发梢乱了点
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不过 这样我们就清爽多了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.86,0:16:16.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,会不会剪太多了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,一点都没变好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 我们下洞看看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,行啊 还能听到水声
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.83,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是下得去吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这里也是遍地的武器
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.21,0:16:45.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前应该发生过激烈的战斗吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这个洞难道也是战斗时留下的？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是从洞的内侧也有炮台这点来看
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.68,0:17:01.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,应该是先有这个洞 然后隔了很久才有那场战斗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,隔了很久？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.79,0:17:09.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没错 这里在很早以前的战争中被打出了一个洞
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.03,0:17:14.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,然后在周围形成城镇后 又发生了战斗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好复杂啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好凉快
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.06,0:17:37.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们去那边吃饭吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.03,0:17:47.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我明明记得当时用白薯烤出了不少食物
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么现在都快没了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不像头发 剪了之后会让人觉得清爽
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这食物少了之后还真够郁闷的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.67,0:17:59.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.84,0:18:04.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要是那个水塘里有鱼就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,鱼吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.76,0:18:10.51,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真想吃水槽里的那条鱼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.69,0:18:16.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,之前你还说想救它的 到头来还是想吃啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是两码事
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,亏你说跟它有了「共感」
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.60,0:18:27.29,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你说 这种洞里会不会冒出食物来啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,既然能流出水
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.44,0:18:39.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.27,0:18:41.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有奇怪的生物
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,生物？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,里面 在这里面
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,生物…是鱼吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.04,0:18:54.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不对 是别的什么
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 你敲一下看看
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.11,0:19:10.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤 没事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,没什么事
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.15,0:19:21.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊 看上去的确不像鱼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.68,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,感觉有在书上看到过
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,会…会是猫吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,猫
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.18,0:19:29.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 吃了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等等 给我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.58,0:19:39.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我说 刚才机器里是不是发出了声音？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊？声音？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊？声…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不会是这家伙在说话吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,这只猫吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道它是不是猫
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 猫 你是只猫吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,它说自己是锚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只是在重复我们的话吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说是锚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.53,0:20:10.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.96,0:20:12.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,烤了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,锚？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.75,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,说了等等
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,还是把它留在这边吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:27.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,会说话的东西叫人怎么吃啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因为有了「共感」吗
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.36,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.85,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,其它好像也没什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.52,0:20:47.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再见啦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.96,0:21:08.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,它好像跟过来了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.70,0:21:24.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 到头来还是要吃了它？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.10,0:21:25.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我们每天都在失去这失去那
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,像这样偶尔增加点什么也挺不错的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.91,0:21:42.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,挺好的 反正它也想跟着我们
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但还是你带着吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我有点怕
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,明明这么可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,别太欺负它
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.77,0:23:37.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.39,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千你唱得真烂
